original_title: Laura Davis: Live at the Easey Street Concert Hall
overview: Smart, original and full of black humour, Aussie Laura Davis brings it all to the table with a combination of well crafted jokes, dark, observational story-telling and provocative themes. From dealing with suicidal tendencies, to that existential life question "Gobby or Shark?" Laura finds the funny when life is giving you a crappy deal.
title: Laura Davis: Live at the Easey Street Concert Hall
